    "ArticleTitle": "Use of an Actinobacillus pleuropneumoniae multiple mutant as a vaccine that allows differentiation of vaccinated and infected animals.",
    "Pagination": {
      "StartPage": "4124",
      "EndPage": "4132",
      "MedlinePgn": "4124-32"
